# Goal: a named mission with ordered GPS waypoints
string mission_id
string[] waypoint_ids
float64[] latitudes
float64[] longitudes
float32 arrival_tolerance_m
bool return_home_after
---
# Result
bool success
string final_waypoint_reached
string failure_reason
float32 total_distance_m
float32 elapsed_seconds
---
# Feedback
ugv_interfaces/DeliveryStatus status
geometry_msgs/Pose current_pose
